[SAY] Same spot. Underscore and caret do the same thing on the current line. Since caret already exists, underscore is redundant.
[SAY] That makes underscore a free key to remap. Some people map it to something useful like toggling a file explorer or switching buffers.
[SAY] With a count like 3 underscore it moves down two lines to the first non-blank. But caret and plus already cover that. Remap it!